Package com.github.yeetmanlord.zeta_core.sql.connection

package com.github.yeetmanlord.zeta_core.sql.connection
Package that manages MySQL database integration. This is only for RAW SQL and I do not recommend using this. SQLHandler could maybe be used but SQLClient doesn't need to be used.
